### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:5550/api/v1
@churchId = church-uuid-here
@subscriptionId = subscription-uuid-here

### Create a subscription
POST {{baseUrl}}/churches/{{churchId}}/subscriptions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "plan": "pro",
  "status": "active",
  "stripePriceId": "price_123"
}

### List subscriptions
GET {{baseUrl}}/churches/{{churchId}}/subscriptions

### Get active subscription
GET {{baseUrl}}/churches/{{churchId}}/subscriptions/active

### Get subscription by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/churches/{{churchId}}/subscriptions/{{subscriptionId}}

### Update subscription
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/churches/{{churchId}}/subscriptions/{{subscriptionId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "plan": "enterprise"
}

### Delete subscription
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/churches/{{churchId}}/subscriptions/{{subscriptionId}}
